quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Zvirokwazvo vatendi ndivo vakabudirira
  23,2,Avo vanoita minamato yavo yose vachitya uye kuzvipira
  23,3,Uye avo vanofuratira manyepo (nehutsvina neizvo zvose zvakarambidzwa naAllah)
  23,4,Uye avo vanopa Zakaah (zvipo kune vanhu vanotambura)
  23,5,Uye avo vanochengetedza nhengo dzavo dzakavandika (kubva mune chehupombwe)
  23,6,"Kunze kune vakadzi vavo kana varanda kadzi avo vavanochengeta vari mumaoko avo, nokudaro vari kure nekushoropodzwa"
  23,7,"Asi uyo anoda zvakadarika izvi, nokudaro avo vatadzi chose (vanopfurikidza mirairo)"
  23,8,Uye avo vanochengetedza zvivimbiso zvavo (zvese zvakakomekedzwa naAllah) uyezve nezvibvumirano zvavo
  23,9,Uye avo vanochengetedza minamato yavo mishanu (5) nenguva dzakatarwa
  23,10,Avo ndivo vagari venhaka yemangwana
  23,11,Vachava vanogara nhaka yeParadhiso (Firdaus). Umo vachagara zvachose
  23,12,Uye zvirokwazvo takave tinosika munhu (Adam) kubva muvhu remutapo (mvura nevhu)
  23,13,Pedzezvo takave tinomuita kuti (vana vaAdam) ave Nutfah (musanganiswa wemvura dzechirume nedzechikadzi uye tikave tinougadzika) panzvimbo yakachengetedzeka (munhumbu yemukadzi)
  23,14,"Pedzezvo takave tinoita Nutfah (musanganiswa wemvura yababa naamai) kuti ive godo reropa, tikave tinoita godo reropa kuti rive chidimbu chenyama, tikave tinogadzira mapfupa kubva muchidimbu chenyama, tikave tinoshongedza mapfupa nenyama, uye tikave tinochiunza sechimwe chisikwa. Naizvozvo makomborero nde aAllah musiki akanaka"
  23,15,"Uye mushure maizvozvo, zvirokwazvo, muchave munofa"
  23,16,"Uye zvirokwazvo, pazuva reQiyaamah (Kumutswa) muchave munomutswa"
  23,17,"Uye zvirokwazvo, takave tinosika pamusoro penyu matenga manomwe (rimwe pamusoro perimwe), uyezve hatimborivari zvisikwa zvedu"